### Create a test roster
POST http://localhost:3000/api/roster
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "driverId": "DRIVER_ID_HERE",
  "vehicleId": "VEHICLE_ID_HERE",
  "startTime": "2025-09-17T09:00:00.000Z",
  "endTime": "2025-09-17T17:00:00.000Z",
  "notes": "Test roster entry"
}

### Get all rosters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/roster
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
